pull_request_body:
You can now add padding inside the chart. This helps with charts that don't have displayed scales, etc. Padding can be specified for all sides of the chart (left, top, right, and bottom).
## Configuration

This adds the same padding on all sides

``` javascript
options: {
  layout: {
    padding: 10
  }
}
```

This version allows different padding on each side

``` javascript
options: {
  layout: {
    padding: {
      // Any unspecified dimensions are assumed to be 0
      left: 10,
      top: 5
    }
  }
}
```

Fixes #3332, #3257 
Replaces #3349

This PR adds a new legend option for filtering items out of the chart legend.

```javascript
options: {
  legend: {
    labels: {
      filter: function(legendItem, chartData) {
        // return false to hide the label
      }
    }
  }
}
```

